{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881831234,"sessionID":"ses_285322a00ffe9paxFH0Id3IOdd","part":{"id":"prt_d7ace1643001KMgYPs0mSUB6Pn","messageID":"msg_d7ace0912001GvlAVe6xWBrKwN","sessionID":"ses_285322a00ffe9paxFH0Id3IOdd","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-c9128307526f47408b42e53bac4ff940","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding)\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-031\n- **Title**: RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding)\n- **Module**: manifests\n- **Language**: YAML\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: Not Started\n\n## Description\n\nRBAC 配置包括 ServiceAccount、Role 和 RoleBinding 的 Kubernetes manifests，用于定义和管理服务账户及其权限。\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Kubernetes cluster\n- Existing manifests structure\n\n## Related Changes\n\nNone\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n[To be filled during implementation]\n\n## Deferred Items\n\n[To be filled during implementation]","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/CHANGE.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/CHANGE.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/CHANGE.md","time":{"start":1775881831215,"end":1775881831233}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881831236,"sessionID":"ses_285322a00ffe9paxFH0Id3IOdd","part":{"id":"prt_d7ace1dec001441t3Ywa8NQwF9","messageID":"msg_d7ace0912001GvlAVe6xWBrKwN","sessionID":"ses_285322a00ffe9paxFH0Id3IOdd","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-51b0cb8ade7249b3b9417ea253fe3bc4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-031 Implementation Notes\n\n## Implementation Status\n- [ ] ServiceAccount manifests\n- [ ] Role manifests\n- [ ] RoleBinding manifests\n- [ ] ClusterRole (if needed)\n- [ ] ClusterRoleBinding (if needed)\n- [ ] RBAC configuration tests\n- [ ] Documentation\n\n## Implementation Details\n\n### Files Created\n\n[To be filled during implementation]\n\n### Test Coverage\n\n[To be filled during implementation]\n\n### RBAC Policy\n\n[To be filled during implementation]\n\n### Notes\n\n[To be filled during implementation]","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/README.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/README.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/README.md","time":{"start":1775881831221,"end":1775881831235}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881831239,"sessionID":"ses_285322a00ffe9paxFH0Id3IOdd","part":{"id":"prt_d7ace4307001IhEZBKVyrPb0Lc","messageID":"msg_d7ace0912001GvlAVe6xWBrKwN","sessionID":"ses_285322a00ffe9paxFH0Id3IOdd","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-eb0cb70279934d4fa818e1a81794a5cf","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) Specification\n\n## Module: manifests\n\n### ServiceAccount\n\n#### ServiceAccount Definition\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: v1\nkind: ServiceAccount\nmetadata:\n  name: <service-account-name>\n  namespace: <namespace>\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `name`: ServiceAccount name\n- `namespace`: Kubernetes namespace\n\n### Role\n\n#### Role Definition\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: Role\nmetadata:\n  name: <role-name>\n  namespace: <namespace>\nrules:\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"pods\", \"services\", \"configmaps\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `name`: Role name\n- `namespace`: Kubernetes namespace\n- `rules`: List of policy rules\n\n### RoleBinding\n\n#### RoleBinding Definition\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: RoleBinding\nmetadata:\n  name: <role-binding-name>\n  namespace: <namespace>\nsubjects:\n  - kind: ServiceAccount\n    name: <service-account-name>\n    namespace: <namespace>\nroleRef:\n  kind: Role\n  name: <role-name>\n  apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `name`: RoleBinding name\n- `namespace`: Kubernetes namespace\n- `subjects`: List of subjects (ServiceAccounts, Users, Groups)\n- `roleRef`: Reference to the Role\n\n### ClusterRole (Optional)\n\n#### ClusterRole Definition\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: ClusterRole\nmetadata:\n  name: <cluster-role-name>\nrules:\n  - apiGroups: [\"\"]\n    resources: [\"nodes\", \"namespaces\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `name`: ClusterRole name\n- `rules`: List of policy rules\n\n### ClusterRoleBinding (Optional)\n\n#### ClusterRoleBinding Definition\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\nkind: ClusterRoleBinding\nmetadata:\n  name: <cluster-role-binding-name>\nsubjects:\n  - kind: ServiceAccount\n    name: <service-account-name>\n    namespace: <namespace>\nroleRef:\n  kind: ClusterRole\n  name: <cluster-role-name>\n  apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `name`: ClusterRoleBinding name\n- `subjects`: List of subjects\n- `roleRef`: Reference to the ClusterRole\n\n## Common API Resources\n\n### Core API (apiGroups: [\"\"])\n\nCommon resources:\n- `pods`\n- `services`\n- `configmaps`\n- `secrets`\n- `persistentvolumeclaims`\n- `events`\n\n### Apps API (apiGroups: [\"apps\"])\n\nCommon resources:\n- `deployments`\n- `statefulsets`\n- `daemonsets`\n- `replicasets`\n\n## Common Verbs\n\n- `get`, `list`, `watch` - Read operations\n- `create` - Create resources\n- `update`, `patch` - Update resources\n- `delete` - Delete resources\n- `*` - All operations\n\n## Best Practices\n\n- Principle of least privilege\n- Namespace-scoped permissions where possible\n- Use specific resource names with `resourceNames` field for fine-grained control\n- Regular review of RBAC policies","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-031/spec.md","time":{"start":1775881831224,"end":1775881831237}}}}
